metadata.name: ALPHA
metadata.description:
α The Beginning

The Metaverse is a 2nd layer scaling solution to 3 Dimensional Reality. 
Metaverse, a Reflection of 3D Reality itself.
3D Reality is already a reflection of the higher Dimensions.
This means the Metaverse is just a different way to have more computational power and extend 3D reality. We should be aware that higher planes and levels of Dimensions might be beyond Death itself.
Consciousness is always connected to higher Dimensions of existence and can retain even higher levels. 5D -> ∞
